        "created_at": "2019-02-14T14:35:57.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"149945\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>At which restaurant did you dine?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>A restaurant in CO - if interested in more info PM me<br>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"149945\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks for the note, Edan, and my condolences that you own only a few bottles of La T\u00e2che.  <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/8/853b6e76c6e8406be77a6727c2a27ad1672678b3.gif\" width=\"31\" height=\"22\" alt=\"[cry.gif]\" title=\"cry\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I appreciate you understanding my plight  <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/b/bdc3944606213c4dca6c1169cf0a166c8bc4f8c9.gif\" width=\"62\" height=\"47\" alt=\"[snort.gif]\" title=\"snort.gif\"><br>\n<br>\n<br></p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"149945\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Curious what you consider \u201ca good price\u201d</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>That\u2019s a loaded question.  The bottle was significantly lower than current wine-searcher lows</p>",
